Please be aware of the of the chronological history of this apartment at this development!

Water Leak,  Mold, Cracks, Vermin, Bugs, flies, and other Housing Code Violations. The maintenance men to come into my home without my permission or knowledge.
They cut a 4x4 square whole the kitchen ceiling without properly securing the safety of my property from damage. I walk-in to dust-filled splattered debris everywhere. No protective plastic sealing was used around the work area.  To be truthfully honest this apartment has never really passed inspection for my family, and I to move into from the very beginning. We were told that the apartment was fully renovated when in fact it was not. Refurbished cabinets, toilet, refrigerator, Air Conditioning/Heating Units  July  2011,
Shortly, after we moved in the "Earthquake" of summer 2011 hit our building as well. My floor and ceiling shifted in opposite directions making a clashing cranking sound. That's when I began to notice all the structural damages not only throughout my apartment but throughout the entire building and then the water leaks began to follow.
Targeted theft activities, One doorman is very "Racist"! He calls the police on people of color in a heart beat!  Prospective Tenants Be Aware!
